<h1>B.C Flooding</h1> 
</h1> This year has been one of climate change with the big wildfires and now the flooding. The community has to step up and do something. We can't just sit back and watch people die, and homes getting trashed. 2021 will be a year to remember. But before we can fight climate change, we have to take care of the B.C floods. Once we are done fighting, the BC floods then we can move on to climate change.</h1>
<a href="https://donate.redcross.ca/page/94172/donate/1?locale=en-CA">Donate to B.C floods today</a> 
