</h1> We need to help because people's homes are getting washed into the river like this is normal. There are houses under water and people need money. All their money was in their houses which are under water. This will be a very costly event. If everyone takes the time to do something small like give someone a little food or donate their old clothes, even if you help fill sandbags. It would help them out a lot. Anything will help in this climate crisis.</h1>
